Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 摇曳百合 开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是赤座灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点冒失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是个元气十足的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个春天成为了初中生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是光鲜亮丽的一年级生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还没有习惯初中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因为有很多新奇的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以每天都忙得团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崭新的校舍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崭新的授课
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崭新的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还处于只要穿上制服就会心跳不已的阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待不已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还赶得上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 勉强safe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 虽然没迟到 但忘记带作业了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.81,0:01:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是作为惩罚 追加了更多作业是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 大概忘在自己桌子上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你睡过头了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我做作业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 卷心菜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因为想着回去的时候要买
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京子你为了不忘记东西也试着这么做一下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 那就赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}灯里酱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:14.92,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我家吗…去啊去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 忘记东西真的很困扰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常忘记到底把什么东西放在房间哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 确实确实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后等到放弃寻找的时候 却轻易地出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 讲到忘记东西我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段时间在电影院里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小魔女米拉库露票一张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉 动画的预售从明天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就跟宣称我是死宅一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对着一无所知的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是何等的耻辱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟忘记东西有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 结衣学姐会去看电影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 偶尔会去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次一起去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有部想看的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千夏酱 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下头发的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这种感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个到底是什么构造啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是从哪聚集起那么多头发的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H3A3B3E&\bord0\pos(640,550)\fs120}京\h\h子\h\h\h的\h\h\h妄\h\h\h想\h\h1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 那个头发到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H3A3B3E&\bord0\pos(640,550)\fs120}京\h\h子\h\h\h的\h\h\h妄\h\h\h想\h\h2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 这个到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能想太多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里想什么被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个零食真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更想吃千夏酱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视她就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休过得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全忘记作业这事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我写在手上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\1c&HF1F1F1&\3c&000000&\fs120\pos(644,500)}放\h\h\h学\h\h\h后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我开始一个人住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…冷…冷面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始做冷面了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎样搞错的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中生一个人住没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有遭到反对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能作为人生经验的一环嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且房东就是亲戚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以家里没怎么反对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也没赞同就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得 好成熟的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\1c&HF1F1F1&\3c&000000&\fs120\pos(644,500)}假\h\h\h日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是京子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 突然之间的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做作业了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便肚子也饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请我吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 给我进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和外观相比 里面出人意料的是个很干净的房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说原本这里是文化中心 经过改造后成住宅了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去 卷心菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就买了啦喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 如此休闲的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采光也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能带枕头来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别住下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么啊那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我幸福又温暖地吃一顿饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那如果灯里她们也还没吃饭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把她们来叫来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 我能吃三人份的饭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁担心这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那你就待在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里说她们到了附近 不过迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去接她们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是原来的文化中心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不是「啥」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了山你当然要说河啊 这是暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得好啊 诸君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就赶紧来搜查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不是要吃午饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京子你不是刚才看过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 在哪一定有新的惊喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在找什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分刺激的决胜内衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种限时出现的东西为什么没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 就综艺节目来说气氛热烈不起来的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就不是综艺节目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真任性啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 京子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能给结衣学姐添麻烦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千夏酱 京子从以前开始就是这副德行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭 饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里觉得蛋包饭比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结衣酱做的蛋包饭很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎好想吃吃看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结衣酱小学三年级就能完美地做出蛋包饭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不完美啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是帮妈妈干活所以记住了做法而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃冧酒提子冰激凌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是你现在想吃而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭吃冧酒提子冰激凌就行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行你个头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰激凌就下次再吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会做好吃的布丁当甜品的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 得寸进尺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎刚才说什么了啊 千夏酱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让学妹们为你费心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冧酒提子冰激凌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结衣大神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 零食要饭后吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结衣酱就像妈妈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 味噌用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买国产的混合味噌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也挺机灵的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快给我去买
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是京子酱买东西回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河啊河啊河啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐亲手做的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都想喝学姐做的味噌汤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千夏酱 结衣是无法保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我的身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明味增是我买来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我觉得不是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\1c&HF0FBF5&\3c&H000000&\fs40\pos(271,147)}说话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\1c&HF0FBF5&\3c&H000000&\fs40\pos(492,147)}魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\1c&HF0FBF5&\3c&H000000&\fs40\pos(277,210)}道具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\1c&HF0FBF5&\3c&H000000&\fs40\pos(506,212)}设定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\1c&HF0FBF5&\3c&H000000&\fs40\pos(277,271)}装备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\1c&HF0FBF5&\3c&H000000&\fs40\pos(459,267)}地图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不是有个卖道具的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 那边有卖药草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是相册
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们小时候 真怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来结衣酱 以前头发很长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学…学姐好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张照片是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京子 来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 结衣酱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 一直很想这么做一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可以呀 结衣酱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 一点都不可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么在你数天花板格子的时候就能结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别进行这种好像真的发生过一样的奇怪妄想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里你也是从小一起长大的 别相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事从以前到现在完全没发生过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…学姐们是从什么时候开始这么要好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…比如说契机什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候开始的来着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为父母关系都很好所以就自然的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也想跟学姐们变得更加要好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千夏酱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 纸巾纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 千夏酱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我觉得我们已经很要好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照哦 千夏酱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么自信能和京子学姐要好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都脏掉了啊 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你洗了 脱下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会给你准备换洗衣物的 去浴室冲个澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会感觉粘糊糊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服上也会沾上污渍的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换洗衣物是结衣学姐的衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许尺寸不太合身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我觉得应该能穿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿 绝对合身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome 千夏酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千夏酱 我会监视这个家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就慢慢冲澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起洗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 给我适可而止…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 竟然穿着睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发现得太晚了 结衣喵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经这么晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里太舒服了 都忘记时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的时候别忘记东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里今后也想经常来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的房间啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 今天多谢款待了 结衣酱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这衣服我会马上洗好还你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦 随便什么时候都行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上会来这里接你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋呢 这个主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冧酒提子冰激凌真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在同一个地方练级呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.61,0:17:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始等级升了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个BOSS就那么厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想等级升得很高 然后轻松打赢BOSS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:18:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我倒是一直都练到要赢不赢的那种等级去挑战的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就会变成拉锯战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且输了的话会很沮丧的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那种极限情况下获胜才好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的打算住下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 睡衣都穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才也和双亲打过电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次大家一起搞个薄烤饼派对之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也许可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把绫乃和千岁也叫过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 确实没跟那两个人一起玩过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我关灯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 晚安的说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这被子 有结衣的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…别闻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻了之后肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会变胖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结衣你不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是最后一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 你吃一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是肚子饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊 我就这么住下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然给你添麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为结衣你外表看起来很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实很怕寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有…这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 我能继续经常过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿京子你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业忘记做了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经早上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京子不好了 要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 京子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我再睡会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来 起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我没带校服过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 灯里 千夏酱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里我也发生过这种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和大家一起上学我就很开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我好好反省
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 京子酱的校服 是不是有点大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我是借结衣的校服穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说得这么自豪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:22:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也借了衣服来着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.41,0:22:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在互相竞争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连没带的教科书也一起借了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 赶紧赶路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是摇曳百合中类似影之主角的船见结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.66,0:23:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然让我来做预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也只是些普通的初中生活基本没有特殊事件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.39,0:23:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回也是 考试 暑假 海边 烟花跟横死的千岁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 都是些常见的事吧